text: Rankweil is a market town in the district of Feldkirch in the Austrian state of Vorarlberg. It is the second largest town in the district of Feldkirch and the eighth largest town in Vorarlberg. Beverage company Rauch is headquartered in Rankweil. == References == == Other websites == * Official website of the market town of Rankweil Category:Settlements in Vorarlberg
